  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64
    Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    ConfigManager
    A class intended to make parsing the config.ini file easier.
    IPFinder
    Console implementation of a class that tries to determine "the IP address" of the machine we're running on.
    IPFinder.IPChooser
    This class uses the interface iterator method below to apply a heuristic that tries to identify "the IP" for the machine we're running on.
    IPFinder.NetworkInterfaceDumper
    A class that prints out the networking environment of the machine.
